docs.lead_paragraph: " If it were not for these high rents," says the young man to himself, "I could get along swimmingly. Good health, a good wife, a good will, and a good business,-but these rents! they eat into my salary frightfully; they consume all the profits, and when I have toiled and tried to the utmost, they bring out a balance against me."

docs.lead_paragraph: " It is a very easy matter to pick out the farmers and out door men from among the members of the Legislature. They look browned and vigorous, as if nature and they were on good terms; while in-door gentry appear as ghostly as spiritual rappers. Health and the plough-handle seem to be in partnership."--Albany Journal.

docs.lead_paragraph: The British and North American Mail steamship Arabia sailed from Liverpool 9:45 A. M., Saturday, 21st May, arrived 12:30 yesterday, making the voyage in 10 days 2 hours 45 minutes. The Humboldt, Capt. LINES, arrived off Cowes on Wednesday night, 18th, and having landed her mails and passengers proceeded on her voyage to Havre.

docs.lead_paragraph: Yesterday witnessed another notable spectacle. The second American Expedition in search of Sir JOHN FRANKLIN, set sail from this port under the command of Dr. E. K. KANE, the Surgeon of the former Expedition.
